OL,3,CStaff member critically injured in
OL,4,Cpetrol station hit-and-run
OL,6,FA staff member at a petrol station is
OL,7,Ffighting for his life after he was hit
OL,8,Fby a car while trying to stop the
OL,9,Fdriver leaving without paying for fuel.
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire Police were called to
OL,12,Fthe Esso petrol station on Castleford
OL,13,FRoad in Normanton at 2.22am on Sunday
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,FThe injured man had been hit by a
OL,17,Fblack Audi after he came out of the
OL,18,Fshop when the driver was driving out
OL,19,Fwithout paying.
