OL,6,FPolice have since arrested an 18-year-
OL,7,Fold man in the Essex area and a 31-
OL,8,Fyear-old in London in connection with
OL,9,Fthe incident.
OL,11,FA vehicle has also been recovered.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Heather Shearer,
OL,14,Fof Wakefield District CID, said: "This
OL,15,Fis an extremely serious incident which
OL,16,Fhas left a man who was doing his job
OL,17,Fin hospital in a critical condition.
